" class=\"w-5 h-5\"></i></a>\n                    <a href=\"https://haroboz.com/mentions-legales/\" class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors\">Mentions légales</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <!-- POPUP -->\n    <div id=\"booking-popup\" class=\"fixed inset-0 z-[100] flex items-center justify-center p-4 popup-hidden\">\n        <div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-brand/60 backdrop-blur-sm\" onclick=\"closePopup()\"></div>\n        <div id=\"popup-content\" class=\"relative bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-2xl max-w-lg w-full max-h-[90vh] overflow-y-auto\">\n            <div class=\"bg-brand rounded-t-2xl p-6 text-center relative\">\n                <button onclick=\"closePopup()\" class=\"absolute top-4 right-4 text-white/70 hover:text-white cursor-pointer\"><i data-lucide=\"x\" class=\"w-6 h-6\"></i></button>\n                <h3 class=\"text-xl font-serif text-white font-bold\">Réservez votre séance</h3>\n                <p class=\"text-white/70 text-sm mt-1\">Réponse confidentielle sous 24h</p>\n            </div>\n            <form id=\"booking-form\" class=\"p-6\" onsubmit=\"handleSubmit(event)\">\n                <div class=\"space-y-4\">\n                    <div>\n                        <label class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-brand mb-1\">Prénom *</label>\n                        <input type=\"text\" required placeholder=\"Votre prénom\" name=\"prenom\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl text-brand placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand focus:border-transparent\">\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                        <label class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-brand mb-1\">Email *</label>\n                        <input type=\"email\" required placeholder=\"votre@email.com\" name=\"email\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl text-brand placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand focus:border-transparent\">\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                        <label class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-brand mb-1\">Téléphone *</label>\n                        <input type=\"tel\" required placeholder=\"06 XX XX XX XX\" name=\"telephone\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl text-brand placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand focus:border-transparent\">\n                    </div>\n                    <div>\n                        <label class=\"block text-sm font-medium text-brand mb-1\">Message</label>\n                        <textarea rows=\"3\" placeholder=\"Parlez-moi de votre projet...\" name=\"message\" class=\"w-full px-4 py-3 border border-gray-200 rounded-xl text-brand placeholder-gray-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-brand focus:border-transparent resize-none\"></textarea>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <button type=\"submit\" class=\"w-full mt-6 bg-brand text-white py-4 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-brand-light transition-colors shadow-lg flex items-center justify-center cursor-pointer\">\n                    <i data-lucide=\"send\" class=\"w-5 h-5 mr-2\"></i> Envoyer ma demande\n                </button>\n                <p class=\"text-center text-xs text-gray-400 mt-3 flex items-center justify-center gap-1\"><i data-lucide=\"lock\" class=\"w-3 h-3\"></i> 100% confidentiel</p>\n            </form>\n            <div id=\"popup-success\" class=\"hidden p-8 text-center\">\n                <div class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4\"><i data-lucide=\"check-circle\" class=\"w-8 h-8 text-green-600\"></i></div>\n                <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-serif text-brand mb-2\">Demande envoyée !</h3>\n                <p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-6\">Je vous recontacte sous 24h.</p>\n                <button onclick=\"closePopup()\" class=\"bg-brand text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-medium hover:bg-brand-light transition-colors cursor-pointer\">Fermer</button>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- FLOATING CTA -->\n    <div id=\"floating-cta\" class=\"fixed bottom-6 right-6 z-50 opacity-0 translate-y-4 transition-all duration-300 pointer-events-none\">\n        <button onclick=\"openPopup()\" class=\"relative bg-brand text-white w-14 h-14 md:w-auto md:h-auto md:px-6 md:py-3 rounded-full shadow-2xl hover:bg-brand-light transition-colors flex items-center justify-center cursor-pointer pulse-ring text-brand\">\n            <i data-lucide=\"calendar\" class=\"w-6 h-6 md:w-5 md:h-5 md:mr-2\"></i>\n            <span class=\"hidden md:inline font-medium\">Prendre RDV</span>\n        </button>\n    </div>\n</div>",
